Package schoolmanagement.commonlib.model

Class CourseEnrollment

java.lang.Object
schoolmanagement.commonlib.model.CourseEnrollment
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class CourseEnrollment extends Object implements Serializable
The CourseEnrollment class represents a student's enrollment in a course, implementing the Serializable interface. It contains information about the student, course, and enrollment date.
Author:
Djordje Ivanovic
